  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 Orthopedic — Tibial Tray Contact Stress Credibility Assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element prediction of tibial tray contact stress in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak contact stress on the tibial polyethylene insert to support a 510(k) substantial-equivalence claim. Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed on material property and boundary-condition inputs. Decision: Accepted.",
